# pastPayloads

**Instance Property**

Returns an array of the daily metrics reports generated since the last allocation of the shared manager instance.

## Declaration

```swift
var pastPayloads: [MXMetricPayload] { get }
```

## Retrieving previous reports

- **pastDiagnosticPayloads**: Returns an array of the diagnostic reports generated since the last allocation of the shared manager instance.
